# Copilot baseline PDFs are processed offline into .md — never read at runtime.
# The 153MB pc12 PDF alone inflated the deploy package to 147MB and broke the
# upload. (firebase.json `ignore` listed it but .gcloudignore overrides that.)
# Scoped to the baselines dir so runtime template PDFs elsewhere are unaffected.
services/copilot/baselines/**/*.pdf
